    "description": "We at Nerolac Select are looking for an experienced Department Manager based out of Patna. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Nerolac Select:\nNerolac Select is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Manage shrinkage and reduce stock discrepancies\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Customer Service\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Nerolac Select!",
